  "headline": "Clipboard API",
  "description": "The Clipboard API (`navigator.clipboard`) provides asynchronous read/write access to the system clipboard from web pages. It replaces `document.execCommand('copy')` with a Promise-based, secure (requires Permissions API) approach supporting text, HTML, images (PNG/SVG), and custom formats.",
